eb.archive.org/web/20180827001033/http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/publications/by-type/yearbook/small-arms-survey-2007.html|archive-date=2018-08-27|url-status=live|author-link=Small Arms Survey}}</ref>\n* [[Republic of the Congo Civil War (1997\u201399)]]<ref name ='SAS 2003'/>\n* [[Iraq War]]<ref name ='SAS 2012 10'>{{cite book|url=http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/publications/by-type/yearbook/small-arms-survey-2012.html|chapter-url=http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/fileadmin/docs/A-Yearbook/2012/eng/Small-Arms-Survey-2012-Chapter-10-EN.pdf|chapter=Surveying the Battlefield: Illicit Arms In Afghanistan, Iraq, and Somalia|title=Small Arms Survey 2012: Moving Targets|publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]]|year=2012|author=Small Arms Survey|page=320|isbn=978-0-521-19714-4|access-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831002411/http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/publications/by-type/yearbook/small-arms-survey-2012.html|archive-date=2018-08-31|url-status=dead|author-link=Small Arms Survey}}</ref>\n* [[Mexican Drug War]]\n* [[Kivu conflict]]<ref name = 'FDLR'/>\n* [[Northern Mali conflict]]<ref name=\"armamentresearch\">{{cite web|url=http://www.armamentresearch.com/small-arms-recovered-in-mali/|title=Small arms recovered in Mali raid &#124; Armament Research Services|publisher=armamentresearch.com|access-date=2015-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020145452/http://armamentresearch.com/small-arms-recovered-in-mali/|archive-date=2015-10-20|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Iraqi Civil War (2014\u20132017)]]\n* [[Syrian Civil War]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3jbNepN6kM |title=Ground Zero: Syria (Part 7) - Snipers of Aleppo - YouTube<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229102532/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3jbNepN6kM |archive-date=2015-12-29 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* [[Yemeni Civil War (2015\u2013present)]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Users==\n<!--READ FIRST: 