s2009\"/>\n*{{flag|Central African Republic}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Importante saisie d'armes en Centrafrique|url=http://www.rfi.fr/afrique/20140315-importante-saisie-armes-centrafrique-rca-misca|language=fr|date=15 March 2014|newspaper=[[Radio France International|RFI]]|access-date=13 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713230556/http://www.rfi.fr/afrique/20140315-importante-saisie-armes-centrafrique-rca-misca|archive-date=13 July 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*{{flag|Chad}}{{citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n*{{flag|Chile}}<ref name=\"Jowett\"/>\n*{{flag|China}}<ref name=\"hogg2002\">Hogg, Ian (2002). ''Jane's Guns Recognition Guide''. Jane's Information Group. {{ISBN|0-00-712760-X}}.</ref> - ceremonial purposes<ref name=sks28/>\n*{{flag|Colombia}}{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*{{flag|Comoros}}<ref name=\"jones2009\"/>\n*{{flag|Congo-Brazzaville}}<ref>{{cite web|language=fr|title=Congo : PCAD - suspension temporaire des op\u00e9rations de collecte d'armes|url=https://reliefweb.int/report/congo/congo-pcad-suspension-temporaire-des-op%C3%A9rations-de-collecte-darmes|date=24 November 2006|access-date=13 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713230832/https://reliefweb.int/report/congo/congo-pcad-suspension-temporaire-des-op%C3%A9rations-de-collecte-darmes|archive-date=13 July 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name ='SAS 2003'>{{cite book|url=http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/publications/by-type/yearbook/small-arms-survey-2003.html|chapter-url=http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/fileadmin/docs/A-Yearbook/2003/en/Small-Arms-Survey-2003-Chapter-08-EN.pdf|chapter=Making the Difference?: Weapon Collection and Small Arms Availability in the Republic of Congo|title=Small Arms Survey 2003: Development Denied|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]]|year=2003|author=Small Arms Survey|pages=267\u2013268|isbn=0199251754|ref={{harvid|Small Arms Survey 2003}}|access-date=2018-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829175229/http://www.smallar